Female student first in 38years to graduate with First class.

A female student of sociology at Ahmadu Bello University, Zaria, has broken a 38-year-old record in her department by graduating with a First Class.


The female student graduated with a CGPA of 4.60. Facebook user, Usman Isah Musa who shared the news, wrote;


Beauty with Brain
Congratulations for breaking 38years record as a First Class Graduate from Sociology Department, Ahmadu Bello University Zaria. This is someone I know personally, I’m specifically proud of you”.












